import React from 'react';
import Proptypes from 'prop-types'
import {Navbar,FormControl,Nav,Form,Button} from 'react-bootstrap'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import Link from 'next/link'
const AppLayout = ({children}) => {
    const NavLeft = styled(Nav)`
    margin-right: 0 !important
    `
    const NavLink = styled(Link)`
    margin: 10px !important
    `
    return (
       <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
        <Navbar.Brand>노드버드</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
            <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                <NavLeft>
                    <NavItem><Link href="/">Home</Link></NavItem>
                    <NavItem><Link href="/profile">프로필</Link></NavItem>
                </NavLeft>
                <Form inline>
                    <FormControl type="text" placeholder="Search" className="mr-sm-2" />
                    <Button variant="outline-success">찾기</Button>
                </Form>
                <NavItem><Link href="/signUp">회원가입</Link></NavItem>
            </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Navbar>
    )
}
AppLayout.proptypes ={
    children: Proptypes.node.isRequired,
}
export default AppLayout
